<div class="pagebreak"></div>

<h2>3) Methodology / Pipeline</h2>
<p>The main pipeline in <code>main_TSMMIS.m</code> executes these steps:</p>
<ol>
  <li><b>Data preparation:</b> load dataset and create unlabeled/few-shot/test sets plus full training pool.</li>
  <li><b>Encoder initialization:</b> use ImageNet-pretrained <code>resnet18</code> when available, otherwise fallback encoder.</li>
  <li><b>Self-supervised pretraining:</b> feature extraction on unlabeled data, normalization, PCA transform, and prototype refinement.</li>
  <li><b>Few-shot evaluation:</b> true N-shot sampling from training pool, prototype classifier training, unlabeled adaptation, test prediction.</li>
  <li><b>Result export:</b> save evaluation MAT file and t-SNE embedding/image outputs.</li>
</ol>

<h2>4) Configuration Summary</h2>
<table>
  <tr><th>Category</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Value</th><th>Source</th></tr>
  <tr><td>Data</td><td>Dataset path</td><td><code>data\NEU-CLS</code></td><td><code>main_TSMMIS.m</code></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Data</td><td>Train ratio</td><td>0.6 (60/40 split)</td><td><code>main_TSMMIS.m</code></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Model</td><td>Classes</td><td>6</td><td><code>main_TSMMIS.m</code></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Model</td><td>Input size</td><td>224 x 224</td><td><code>main_TSMMIS.m</code></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Pretraining</td><td>Epochs</td><td>300</td><td><code>main_TSMMIS.m</code></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Pretraining</td><td>Batch size</td><td>64</td><td><code>main_TSMMIS.m</code></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Pretraining</td><td>Learning rate</td><td>0.003</td><td><code>main_TSMMIS.m</code></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Pretraining</td><td>PCA dim</td><td>256</td><td><code>main_TSMMIS.m</code></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Few-shot</td><td>Label counts</td><td>[1, 2, 3, 4]</td><td><code>main_TSMMIS.m</code></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Few-shot</td><td>Runs per setting</td><td>100</td><td><code>main_TSMMIS.m</code></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Few-shot</td><td>Self-train iterations</td><td>2</td><td><code>main_TSMMIS.m</code></td></tr>
  <tr><td>Few-shot</td><td>Self-train margin</td><td>0.08</td><td><code>main_TSMMIS.m</code></td></tr>
</table>

<h2>5) Experimental Results</h2>
<p>Reported project results from the provided project documentation:</p>
<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Setting</th>
    <th>Labels per Class</th>
    <th>Mean Accuracy</th>
    <th>Std Dev</th>
  </tr>
  <tr><td>1-shot</td><td>1</td><td>88.13%</td><td>4.68%</td></tr>
  <tr><td>2-shot</td><td>2</td><td>93.11%</td><td>2.64%</td></tr>
  <tr><td>3-shot</td><td>3</td><td>94.86%</td><td>1.85%</td></tr>
  <tr><td>4-shot</td><td>4</td><td>95.75%</td><td>1.51%</td></tr>
</table>
<p>
Trend in project results: accuracy increases and variance decreases as labeled support per class grows from 1 to 4.
</p>

