<h2>8) Conclusion</h2>
<p>
This report summarizes the TSMMIS MATLAB project using only in-repository information and assets. The current implementation
shows strong few-shot performance on NEU-CLS with best reported accuracy of <b>95.75% at 4-shot</b> and robust
<b>88.13% at 1-shot</b>, with the corresponding t-SNE result and dataset sample images included from the project files.
</p>

